{"tid":1314249,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 重開 ] 沙田 即時地圖 測試版","createTime":"2019-07-14T05:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T08:19:17.000Z","uid":52105,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a90d0d8bdd877e9035236398e601bf92812eb579","tid":1314249,"uid":52105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T05:52:14.000Z","msg":"sorry頭先唔記得揀台就開post<br />\n錯post：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1314172/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1314172/page/1</a><br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n[ 實時更新 Google Map 第一版 ]<br />\n<a href=\"https://pluvia-map.firebaseapp.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpluvia-map.firebaseapp.com&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPakHQxt1T4ELL4DwIHxiqIsg%3D&h=83bb5835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pluvia-map.firebaseapp.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://pluvia-map.firebaseapp.com/maps/sha-tin\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpluvia-map.firebaseapp.com%2Fmaps%2Fsha-tin&d=05%2BDYq1PAX1syIB%2FutXPakHQxt1T4ELL4DwIHxiqIsg%3D&h=c8f37858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pluvia-map.firebaseapp.com/maps/sha-tin</a><br />\n<br />\n是咁的一星期前我開post話要整個即時更新地圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1293568/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1293568/page/1</a><br />\n能力有限，但總叫有舊野玩下<br />\n呢個版本目的旨在做 Proof of Concept<br />\n去俾\b大眾感受即時更新地圖戰係咩野玩法<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Real-time</span></strong>係重點，所以user唔login都可以加 Marker<br />\nSecurity 我只係做左最低限度設定<br />\n所以<span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好信</span>地圖上面嘅Marker<br />\n<br />\n網頁有以下功能可以玩：<br />\n1. 主頁個Like制無限㩒，亦會即時更新其他人㩒<br />\n2. 地圖頁㩒落去會可以俾你加Marker，暫時只係揀左5個Marker玩<br />\n3. 只會顯示 last 100 Marker，因為唔想overload大家部手機<br />\n<br />\n已知問題：<br />\n- 手機版網頁移哂位，iPhone SE連個制都㩒唔到<br />\n<br />\n小弟真心覺得呢個網頁可以搞大佢<br />\n謹此跪求各位連登仔幫手做壓力測試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果反應好嘅話我會繼續寫落去 <br />\n<br />\nbetween, sorry for 1999<br />\n琴晚通左頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37d5d1f834d8772cca6ba03d94f903377c9b333f","tid":1314249,"uid":31974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d69f7211a97ed7677a4e90373bf2bb94613cf64","tid":1314249,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"927001a089982c5684d8d66418c0449104752199","tid":1314249,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:13:03.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1763271603595ecff77f8c0e3fa69c6f04f028cc","tid":1314249,"uid":125680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"推左先"},{"pid":"2ad05fac1a002c58018a59a7dce0555a6e6cbb75","tid":1314249,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:13:10.000Z","msg":"重要技術 多謝巴打"},{"pid":"64553655cddbfb637ec4897ed5e3c3d379a87c3f","tid":1314249,"uid":2189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:13:48.000Z","msg":"推，好有用"},{"pid":"974d640e2680beed329df4a66a6951fc46e3ce66","tid":1314249,"uid":2189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:40:08.000Z","msg":"推返上黎"},{"pid":"06c7ab1d50aef829dbc0ed41c671ce7bc929d777","tid":1314249,"uid":196114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T06:41:21.000Z","msg":"推 ！感激手足！"},{"pid":"2f5d617e130a67b2123ff615d455fe92d1bb4871","tid":1314249,"uid":45486,"like":0,"disli